{"type": "article", "id": 4487, "title": "Offiseria 帆船台灯", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-18T07:41:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233556OMfoHWrURcaFKNLp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t意大利生活家居品牌 Offiseria 日前邀请意大利设计工作室 Mario Alessiani 为其设计了一款帆船系列的台灯 Vela，仅使用了折叠与激光切割的加工方式，创造了一个简单的金属结构。按照 Offiseria 提出的造价低廉的要求，设计师运用激光切割的桶状结构将灯泡固定在适当的位置，然后配置以小型的合金薄板调整光传播的方向，最终呈现出一个极简的稳定轻薄结构的台灯。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233554TfJRGuZijOr6cFzH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233555j4ZnYSNBLxJThE6s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052335557YLmXsCSrp4v3qnu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233556KtUnheMN0HiSXyvD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233556sKxuvUp5tH7y3Pce.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}